de.charite.compbio.jannovar.pedigree.compatibilitychecker

Interface InterfaceVariantContextCompatibilityChecker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractVariantContextCompatibilityChecker, VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerAutosomalDominant, VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerAutosomalRecessive, VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerAutosomalRecessiveCompoundHet, VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerAutosomalRecessiveHomozygous, VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerXDominant, VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerXRecessive

    public interface InterfaceVariantContextCompatibilityChecker
    Interface for a VariantContextCompatibilityChecker. The have two modes. A single sample run and a multi sample run. the general method run() will decide if it is a singe sample or a multi sample.
    Version:
    0.15-SNAPSHOT
    Author:
    Max Schubach
